This is Dr. George W. Kirchwey, Warden of Sing Sing for six month, see <a href="http://chroniclingamerica.loc.gov/lccn/sn83030214/1916-07-16/ed-1/seq-37/" rel="nofollow">New-York tribune., July 16, 1916, Page 5</a> (with photo). He was dean of Columbia Law school before.

&quot;George Washington Kirchwey (July 3, 1855 Detroit, Michigan - March 3, 1942) was an American lawyer, politician, journalist and legal scholar.&quot;
